  "title": "QA Assistant (Logistics & Packaging)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Review and validate daily QC inspection reports (Kizeo) to ensure compliance with documentation standards.</li>\n  <li>Manage and update quality documentation, including revising work instructions as needed.</li>\n  <li>Adjust department work instructions based on workflow changes or customer requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Role Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate with operations, admin, logistics, and QC teams.</li>\n  <li>Verify accuracy of QC reports and maintain training/qualification records.</li>\n  <li>Support QC inspections when required and handle SAP Y7/Y8 for non-conformance crates.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and present weekly/monthly QA validation reports.</li>\n  <li>Perform other ad hoc tasks as assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or equivalent with at least 1 year of warehouse experience</li>\n  <li>Proficient in MS Office (Word, Excel, Outlook)</li>\n  <li>Able to work accurately in a fast-paced environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | 20C0270</p>\n<p>Tew Jie Wei | R22016822</p>",
